    "If this screening step is successful, Stage Two of the DA scheme constructs p",
    "enkf,t (y 0:t |x *,1:N 0:t) and the Stage Two acceptance probability",
    "Thus the overall acceptance probability for the scheme is α 1 α 2|1 and standard arguments show that iterating the DA scheme defines a Markov chain that is reversible with respect to the (extended) target π enkf,t (θ, x1:N 0:t, x 1:N 0:t |y 0:t).",
    "It has been assumed that the density, f",
    "t (•|x), arising from the observation model is a linear and Gaussian conditional density; see (8)."
